Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…黄泉…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前的那天  我遇见了生命中重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  请注意脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前的那天  我遇见了那个沉浸在悲伤中的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个大雨倾盆雾霭弥漫的午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次同样背负着宿命的两人的命运的相会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切故事的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N「邂逅之际」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫大人  土宫大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务对我们退魔师一族来说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至对于所有的圣者来说都是重大的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然击败了怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但土宫大人的夫人却不幸遇害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫大人当前正在进行将从夫人那继承来的的喰灵白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（白叡：被称为狗神的灵兽。白毛狗头以及似龙的长脖、身体各处缠绕着锁链。\N作为「吞食恶灵的恶灵这一被诅咒的最终兵器」封印在神乐家族祖先体内。）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与自己的灵魂融为一体的封印仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前土宫大人一直作为盟主调和各个分家的事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但寄宿了喰灵后就要全身心地专注于除灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故而今后就由我谏山奈落担此重任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请诸位助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐你旁边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫神乐小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我叫谏山黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲作为土宫家第27代当家继承了白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你母亲从上代继承下来的传承了数百年的重大使命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于迟早将接过这权杖的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为分家一员的我会负责在暗中支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替你那事务繁忙的父亲  你的生活起居将由我家照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了  神乐妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了不少啊  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得以前到这里来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事  那时你还太小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得也是人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲在分家会议之后不是还说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心自己能否胜任退魔师首领这样的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使命如此光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么理不直气不壮就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必有所拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你父亲是老相识了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这当自己家一样放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来  神乐妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就住这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始这就是你房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去搬行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会派车过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用跟我客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这住上一段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有些必需品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书啊  游戏啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间虽然稍稍有些乱  不用太拘谨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁好呢还是茶好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我泡茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒出些零食吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薯片吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借用一下…道场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  有得到土宫大人真传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素质不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我陪你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  全力攻过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你这年纪来说刀法算很快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加以磨练会更强的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了就是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  神乐妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想得这么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再努力就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战中没有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  还算很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说过实战中不能选择对手的强弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了就意味着死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有使命的人死了就会导致上百个无辜的人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们生为退魔师要对自己的生命负责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲再三叮嘱过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是练习  输了也要深刻反省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐妹妹的父亲非常古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不止  外加性情乖僻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是赢还是输
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到夸奖就该会心地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到你陪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐妹妹讨厌吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不要挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  肯定有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…皮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  输了的话今晚的配菜就是蔬菜炒皮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐妹妹赢了就给你做喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没准备好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏也是输了就是输了  不能等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样…太狡猾了  黄泉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用「小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的好吃吧  皮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天也做皮蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了神乐妹妹  来我房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在习惯之前一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去换睡衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（母亲的病情并不乐观。尽快赶到医院。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉姐姐的母亲生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是集合口令而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就算是上课时之类的也不得不脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合口令？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作  虽然现在还是打工阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  可能会很晚  你先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理班出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计到达现场时间为2100
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这是上个月飞机失事死亡的海外派遣队伍的活动记录
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长三途河教授似乎在梵蒂冈搜寻着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三途河教授  是使用巫蛊术的家系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（巫蛊为一种操纵毒虫，并以咒诅害人的巫术，也叫蛊、蛊术。属于黑巫术的一种。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他研究的主题是  杀生石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（杀生石：千年前、被阴阳师收伏的封印着九尾之魂的妖力的结晶。\N一旦植入人体，虽然能得到无限的妖力，作为代价灵魂会被侵蚀导致肉体毁灭化为恶灵。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽然经过外务省询问过相关负责人士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是没有得到明确的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  继续进行调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  再来是关于前几天除灵作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾还没有完全确认已被净化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然怨灵消失踪迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还没有确凿证据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个即使有着喰灵白叡也陷入苦战的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下祸根就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是微小的残留思念也不要放过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚接任就这么多辣手事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆也真是挑了个棘手的时间交接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校怎么样  开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天物理课上学支点  力点  作用点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习至关重要  趁年轻要好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  神乐妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为昨天赔礼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做你喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油可乐饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油可乐饼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个很费事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  做吧  奶油可乐饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐妹妹也能来帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去趟超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  神乐妹妹  叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人认识路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  回来晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该…不会太迟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我也说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我等着  说是马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  乖乖的等着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着她能快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…妈妈却
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会抛下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看看我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  不想看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓着她啊  岩端先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样子很吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私自让平民看到绝密任务…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是土宫神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宫…难道是那个土宫家的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是纳布先生和纳布先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布也初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是孪生兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是哥哥纳布  一个是弟弟纳布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取一样的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这似乎是出生地的风俗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是新人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是樱庭一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来年纪小了点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这行人手实在不够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是饭纲纪之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算人手足够也照样欢迎年轻女性加盟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有其它想法的话我可不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然知道  我眼里只有黄泉你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空压式·退魔居合刀舞蹴拾贰号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（出自名匠迈克尔小原之手的会选择使用者的退魔刀，\N剑辅最初使用的武器。其威力会随着使用者的灵力而变化）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天从师傅那送达的新作品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  岩端先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是土宫家的孩子的话  用这个是绰绰有余吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽刀时拉动扳机的话  依靠压缩空气力量能使出刀威力达到平时的3倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是不该带她来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策室致处理班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是处理班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情报  当前超自然灾害源出现在千代田区神田附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速应对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是出身土宫家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是昨天的残余
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁它被封印在结界里  赶快处理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正苏醒了可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着  神乐妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是环境省自然环境局超自然灾害对策室的处理班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理掉在人世间作恶的恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及对人类持有怨恨的怨灵是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵺？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿于黄泉的宝刀狮子王上的灵兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:42.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（寄宿在宝刀狮子王里的灵兽。酷似红色狮子的巨大野兽、尾部是无数的蛇。\N仍然跟随在恶灵化后的黄泉左右。名字叫乱红莲。）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵兽  鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把代为照顾的大小姐带到这么危险的任务里去  到底作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你强烈要求下我才同意接她过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么擅自妄为可不轻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹他生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家常便饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于刚才的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的强烈要求下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是想要个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐妹妹不想有姐妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  但是对方是黄泉姐姐就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就成为姐妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  从今天开始神乐就是我手下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不是妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对姐姐来说妹妹就相当于手下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你  是护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  作为交换等神乐再长大点才能做那工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然父亲又要大发雷霆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能被责骂真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和父亲不怎么交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行的时候很严厉  但除此之外就不怎么说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  但能和亲生父亲一起生活真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的双亲在我小时候被怨灵取走了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把杀死双亲的怨灵消灭的就是现在的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谏山家的养女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谏山家代代相传的宝刀  狮子王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲却把它传给了没有血缘关系的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当成真正的女儿抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也打算好好地报答他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继承谏山的宿命——身为退魔师的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命  使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这就是我存在的全部意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:21:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;6;0;0,（咒文大意：不动明王慈救咒  曩莫三曼多缚日罗赧  战拏摩诃路洒拏  萨颇咤也  吽  怛罗迦  悍漫  嚩多他  欠  佉呬）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}namah samanta vajrânâm canda
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}mahâ rosana sphataya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}hûm traka hâm mâm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}vâtatha kham khahi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  医院来消息说妈妈的病情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去吧  祝早日康复
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课叫你出来不好意思啊  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都对老师撒谎真过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留着口水的痕迹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的神乐怪脸收藏又多了一张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种收藏最好删了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄～泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加速了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:28.93,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる瞳が　痛みを映したら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:31.18,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向いてごらん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:34.20,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}情熱放つTrick
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:40.49,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}崩れる足元　二人は戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:45.57,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}差し伸べた手をほどかないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:51.84,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}消えるよまた　やさしい日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:57.07,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出を汚すのは許せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.62,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここは裏切りの楽園（ティル{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK}·{\r}ナ{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK}·{\r}ノーグ）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.24,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さ迷う心の涯に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:09.17,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光を求めて　祈る言葉届けあなたに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.22,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}囚われの羽が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:14.87,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遥かな空へと向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:20.81,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じたいよ　私たち孤独じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.61,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分かり合う（求め合う）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:26.46,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}絆の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:29.39,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}離さない（離れない）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:32.98,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}始まるDestiny
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:28.93,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}当圣洁的眼眸　映出痛苦之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:31.18,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}回首遥望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:34.20,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}热情奔放Trick
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:40.49,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}崩溃的脚下　无法返回的二人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:45.57,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}不要将伸来的手松开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:51.84,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那温暖的日子　将再次消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:57.07,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}决不允许将思念污染
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.62,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这里是背叛的乐园{\fnArial\fe1}（Tír Na nóg）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.24,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在彷徨的心灵深处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:09.17,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追寻光明　将祝福的话语传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.22,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被束缚的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:14.87,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奔向那遥远的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:20.81,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要相信　我们并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.61,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}互相理解（互相追求）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:26.46,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那羁绊之中
